Ignacio Perez
ABDT project

Classification for tweets. 

Using a Naive Bayes classificator written in PIG, this project is capable to assign categories to a set of tweets, 
using a preclassified set of tweets.

It as also retrieving the Klout score to classify conversations. 


Pig Files: working and tested wit PIG 0.10
Java Files: no ant nor maven, .sh scripts to compile and execute.



